WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:02.500
Wow...

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.000
They're huge.

3
00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:07.000
They are.

4
00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.500
See that one?

5
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.000
